views.markdown: If you need help with "TextChanger", you can contact Jayden Letourneau, the developer, via e-mail.
Jayden Letourneau is the maintainer of the package "TextChanger". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "Jaydenn's Repo" repo, Jayden.
